*Vlasti* su odlučile da proglase vanredno stanje. (The authorities decided to declare a state of emergency.)

Izbori su odlučili *vlasti* u zemlji. (The elections determined the authorities in the country.)

Lokalne *vlasti* su odlučile da investiraju u obrazovanje. (The local authorities decided to invest in education.)

Građani su se obratili *vlastima* zbog pogoršanja uslova života. (The citizens appealed to the authorities due to the deterioration of living conditions.)

*Vlastima* je bilo teško da preduzmu neophodne mere. (It was difficult for the authorities to take the necessary measures.)